Business Process Analyst
-
Date Posted: 2014/05/06 06:00:20
Ref. JB3047700
Job Description
An experienced Business Process Analyst is sought on a full time permanent basis by one of the largest banks in United Arab Emirates. This will directly be reporting to the Businessn Process Manager under the Enterprise Projects and Architecture.Job holder will assist in reviewing/developing and re-engineering business processes by working closely with Business and Support Division colleagues to understand and document business processes. This will include making recommendations to enhance the efficiency of processes that span several functional work areas. This is a genuine opportunity to work for one of the largest banks in the Gulf region in addition to exploring a great opportunity to earn tax-free income in a growing economyTo be able to qualify for the said role, you need to meet the following requirements: - Relevant experience in Business Process Management- Experience of process management/process re-engineering and workflow automation is desirable (preferably supported by a recognized Process Management qualification)- Project Management experience- banking / financial services sector experience is desirable- international exposure is advantageousIf you meet the criteria and interested to explore this career, please revert back with your updated CV in strictest of confidence and get in touch directly with Chawen Yan at Huxley Associates. Sthree UAE is acting as an Employment Agency in relation to this vacancy.
Skills
To be able to qualify for the said role, you need to meet the following requirements:
- Relevant experience in Business Process Management
- Experience of process management/process re-engineering and workflow automation is desirable (preferably supported by a recognized Process Management qualification)
- Project Management experience
- banking / financial services sector experience is desirable
- international exposure is advantageous
